{
  "name": "IET - Appointment Confirmation & Prep Sequence",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Workflow 4: Appointment Confirmation & Prep Sequence\n\n**Trigger:** Webhook POST from AppTotal booking confirmation\n\n**Required payload:**\n- customer_name, customer_email, customer_phone\n- appointment_date (YYYY-MM-DD)\n- appointment_time (HH:MM, 24h)\n- service_type: mold | air_quality | emf | chemical | multi\n- inspector_name\n- property_address\n\n**Sequence:**\n1. Immediate confirmation email + SMS\n2. 48-hour reminder with service-specific prep instructions\n3. Day-of reminder 2 hours before\n4. Trigger review request workflow post-inspection\n5. Log all events to Google Sheets\n\n**IMPORTANT:** Update YOUR_WORKFLOW_01_WEBHOOK_URL to point to Workflow 1's webhook URL.",
        "height": 360,
        "width": 440
      },
      "id": "wf4-0001-aaaa-bbbb-cccc-000000000001",
      "name": "Sticky Note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [0, 0]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "httpMethod": "POST",
        "path": "iet-appointment-booked",
        "responseMode": "immediately",
        "responseData": "allEntries"
      },
      "id": "wf4-0002-aaaa-bbbb-cccc-000000000002",
      "name": "Webhook - Receive AppTotal Booking",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [500, 400],
      "webhookId": "iet-apptotal-booking-webhook"
    },
    {
